The defendant Anthony Lee Mau was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Anthony Lee Mau is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Anthony Lee Mau was found guilty of Fail to Register Deer, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 29.347(2).

  • Anthony Lee Mau was found guilty of Possess Firearm-Convicted of a Felony, a class G felony, Wisconsin Statutes 941.29(1m)(a).
  • Anthony Lee Mau was found guilty of Possess Deer during Closed Season, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 29.055.

Court questions attorney Sauder  re: her clients plea and waiver of rights.

-Concurrent with 1, 2, 3, 8 & 9

Dismiss counts 4, 5 & 7.
So ordered.
